      "text": [
        "4160 - وَ سَأَلَهُ اَلْحَلَبِيُّ : عَنْ صَيْدِ اَلْحِيتَانِ وَ إِنْ لَمْ يُسَمَّ فَقَالَ \"لاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4160 - Al-Halabi asked him about catching fish without mentioning the name of Allah (swt) over it.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it.\""
        ]
      }
    }
